game.name: Minnie Mouse Cupcakes
game.description:
Minnie Mouse Cupcakes is an excellent cooking game for girls where you will get a chance to try a new dessert recipe. The preparation of this recipe requires several great ingredients. Follow the recipe instructions properly to create delicious cupcakes in the shortest possible time. Join this free online cooking game to have fun together with some of your favourite characters. Known as one of the most in-demand Disney characters, Minnie Mouse is the main character of this game. 

This pretty girl has decided to prepare her special cupcakes, for which she has to collect the needful ingredients first. No need to bother how to go for it since she will be there all the time providing you with the necessary instructions. After collecting the ingredients, start preparing the recipe with the help of mouse. Take a bowl and mix some salt, baking powder, sugar and flour in it. Make the composition using the hand mixer you will see in the kitchen. 

Take another bowl and put some eggs in it. Add vanilla, milk and butter and mix this composition. Collect a tray and place the cupcake composition in it with the help of a small spoon. Congratulations! Your scrumptious dessert dish is ready to be served. Play this brand new cooking game for girls and boys again and again to have fun in your vacant periods. Do not worry if the goal of the game does not achieve in the first attempt, various chances are available to help complete the mission of this cool html5 game.
